title: Feature-Based-Starter-TPOT-LB0.559+
description: This notebook goes through a simple process of extracting usable columns, append decomposition components to the data set, generating a few basic features, building a model and then make predictions. I am using the TPOT package to create a pipeline. TPOT is a Python Automated Machine Learning tool that optimizes machine learning pipelines using genetic programming.  I thought it is useful to add this to the list of kernels available in this competition.
